        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 11. Micrographs of Bryodrilus diverticulatus Černosvitov, 1929. A. Brain. B. Ventral chaetae. C. Segments VI–XI. D. Oesophageal appendages. E–G. Sperm funnels. H, I. Pharyngeal glands, spermathecae (marked with white arrows) and oesophageal appendages (marked with black arrows). B–E, G–I in vivo, A, F fixed, stained. Scale bars 50 μm, C 100 μm." ;
